com.aliyun.oss.model

类 ResponseHeaderOverrides

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aliyun.oss.model.ResponseHeaderOverrides

  • public class ResponseHeaderOverrides
extends Object
    The class wraps the HTTP Get response headers to override. For Response headers, please refer to https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/31980.html?spm=5176.doc31980.6.870. zfxavo Basically it tells the OSS to return the specified headers in the response.
